results.name: G.f.: Sum_{k>=1} (-1)^(k + 1) * k * x^(k*(k + 1)) / (1 - x^k).
comment: Excess of sum of odd divisors of n that are < sqrt(n) over sum of even divisors of n that are < sqrt(n).
mathematica: nmax = 80; CoefficientList[Series[Sum[(-1)^(k + 1) k x^(k (k + 1))/(1 - x^k), {k, 1, nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x] // Rest
